::Firaxis/Horn::
       He replies to her message.  "Relax, I said I'm on my way and I'm 
almost to your position."  He bows formally.  "I have arrived.  And this is 
my dog Horn."  He pats Horn on the head.  Horn barks and starts panting.  "I 
am glad to hear that you have thought some more about what I said."

--part1_7e.288bceba.2a301a5f_boundary
